description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps the weekend in sports. Are there benefits to professionals boxing social media influencers? What are the Nets Chances if James HArden is out for an extended period of time? Nets Studio host Frank Isola joins us to discuss. Reggie Miller calls in for his weekly spot to preview the Jazz/Clippers series.
